OL,7,FThe trial began in Coleraine last
OL,8,Fmonth, but just one day later,
OL,9,FCreswell was found dead. The coroner
OL,10,Fhas been informed and his death is not
OL,11,Fbeing treated as suspicious.
OL,13,FKerry McKenzie knew Creswell better
OL,14,Fthan most.
OL,16,FThey ended up sharing stables in Co
OL,17,FArmagh for two years, after his
OL,18,Frelease from prison following an
OL,19,Fhorrific attack on a previous
OL,20,Fgirlfriend.
