OL,3,CThe dark side of suspected killer:
OL,4,CComing face-to-face with Jonathan
OL,5,CCreswell
OL,7,FShe witnessed outbursts towards Katie,
OL,8,Fwho was just a teenager then.
OL,10,F"In an indoor school one evening, I
OL,11,Fcould hear the screaming and shouting,
OL,12,FJonny was screaming and shouting at
OL,13,Fher," said Kerry McKenzie.
OL,15,F"There used to be a wee hole at the
OL,16,Fend of the indoor school and we went
OL,17,Fdown and had a peep through it, and
OL,18,FJonny was literally chasing her around
OL,19,Fwith a blue pipe in his hand shouting,
OL,20,Fscreaming, calling her all the names
OL,21,Fof the day.
