OL,3,CThe dark side of suspected killer:
OL,4,CComing face-to-face with Jonathan
OL,5,CCreswell
OL,7,F"It was absolutely horrific, it got to
OL,8,Fthe stage where he was running around
OL,9,Fscreaming at her, he actually threw
OL,10,Fthe blue pipe when she was riding down
OL,11,Fpast him on the horse."
OL,13,FKerry even had to defend herself
OL,14,Fagainst Creswell with a pitchfork
OL,15,Fduring a heated row.
OL,17,FShe said: "He was spitting through his
OL,18,Fteeth, to the point that he came right
OL,19,Fup into my nose, and he was 'going to
OL,20,Fdo this' and he was 'going to do that'.
