OL,7,F"Luckily I had the pitchfork in my
OL,8,Fhand I just lifted it up and I turned
OL,9,Fit around so the forks were touching
OL,10,Fon his face and I just said 'Jonny,
OL,11,Fyou're going to do nothing'."
OL,13,FKatie Simpson died following an
OL,14,Fincident in Gortnessy Meadows,
OL,15,FLettershandoney, on 3 August 2020.
OL,17,FKerry McKenzie didn't buy Jonathan
OL,18,FCreswell's claims of suicide,
OL,19,Fcontacting police just after the
OL,20,Ffuneral.
